Heading: Introducing our first card game: Jig!\
\
Body: Jig is a competitive game of memory, deduction, and revenge! Fish for cards from the opposing team, paying attention to what other players ask for and what they get. When you think your team has all the cards of one colour, you can \'93land\'94 them \'96\'96 but you must know exactly who has which cards, or else the other team steals the point!\
\
Coming late 2026 / early 2027!\
\
